Feature: This suite will verify search and purchase using Debit card

Background:
	Given  User is on login page
    When   User enters username

Scenario: Verify search and purchase using valid VISA debit card
When    User enters password
And    User clicks on signin button
Then   User should be on home page
And    User should get welcome message
When   User enters search data
And    USer clicks on search button
Then   User should get search result

